 singing like a psalm"},{"s":53.84,"e":56.28,"text":"You can stack your steel up high"},{"s":56.38,"e":57.8,"text":"But the truth won’t stay denied"},{"s":57.8,"e":57.8,"text":"If the light gets blocked"},{"s":57.8,"e":59.28,"text":"The towers rise"},{"s":60.64,"e":63.22,"text":"If the light gets blocked"},{"s":63.6,"e":66.04,"text":"The towers rise"},{"s":70.68,"e":72.96,"text":"St. John’s still speaks"},{"s":72.96,"e":75.34,"text":"Through dust and signs"},{"s":75.42,"e":78.18,"text":"St. John’s Soup Kitchen"},{"s":78.18,"e":83.1,"text":"Covered with prophecy"},{"s":85.82,"e":93.06,"text":"On Market steps and chipped stone stairs"},{"s":94.7,"e":97.76,"text":"People bring their hunger there"},{"s":98.72,"e":102.22,"text":"Soup in bowls and folded coats"},{"s":103.44,"e":107,"text":"Quiet prayers in battered notes"},{"s":108.42,"e":110.32,"text":"If the watchers crowd the sky"},{"s":110.32,"e":112.88,"text":"And seal the morning from our eyes"},{"s":112.9,"e":115.26,"text":"There’s a name carved deep in time"},{"s":115.26,"e":117.58,"text":"And it won’t be erased tonight"},{"s":117.66,"e":119.88,"text":"You can pad the dark with stone"},{"s":120.04,"e":122.26,"text":"You can name the night your own"},{"s":122.26,"e":124.64,"text":"But the old bells know the way"},{"s":124.64,"e":126.16,"text":"Through the fear and through the gray"},{"s":126.16,"e":126.16,"text":"If the light gets blocked"},{"s":126.16,"e":128.74,"text":"The towers rise"},{"s":129.28,"e":131.6,"text":"If the light gets blocked"},{"s":131.76,"e":134.38,"text":"The towers rise"},{"s":139.44,"e":141.22,"text":"St. John’s still speaks"},{"s":141.22,"e":143.7,"text":"Through dust and signs"},{"s":143.78,"e":146.42,"text":"St. John’s Soup Kitchen"},{"s":147.56,"e":148.84,"text":"Covered with prophecy"},{"s":162.84,"e":167.18,"text":"Let the first red ray come back"},{"s":167.18,"e":172.24,"text":"Over soot and broken tracks"},{"s":172.7,"e":176.5,"text":"What was fed to every soul"},{"s":176.58,"e":180.78,"text":"Will not be lost to what they hold"},{"s":181.1,"e":184.6,"text":"And if they build, let them build"},{"s":185.48,"e":189.24,"text":"The old words outlast the chill"},{"s":189.92,"e":194.2,"text":"I hear Newark say it clear"},{"s":194.94,"e":199.52,"text":"The dawn is still here"},{"s":201.4,"e":204.3,"text":"If the light gets blocked"},{"s":204.44,"e":206.6,"text":"The towers rise"},{"s":207.16,"e":208.9,"text":"If the light gets blocked"},{"s":209.86,"e":211.88,"text":"The towers rise"},{"s":211.98,"e":213.92,"text":"St. John’s still speaks"},{"s":213.92,"e":216.26,"text":"Through dust and signs"},{"s":216.42,"e":219.02,"text":"St. John’s Soup Kitchen"},{"s":220.22,"e":221.54,"text":"Covered with prophecy"},{"s":224.04,"e":226.86,"text":"Covered with prophecy"},{"s":229.78,"e":231.02,"text":"Covered with prophecy"}],"duration":242.4,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.242Z","stats":{"whisperWords":290,"polishedWords":309,"matched":266,"matchRate":0.861}}